title: Shape5 S5 TheClassifieds Joomla 2.5-3.x Template
description:
The most comprehensive directory template designed for Joomla is here. The new Classifieds Ads template is your perfect choice for creating an online listings directory. The directory is powered by the Joomanager component purchased separately at http://www.joomanager.com. The directory offers features including, ratings, paid ads, Google map search and unlimited searchable custom fields and much more! Although the template is geared for a directory style site keep in mind it can be used for any website. Check out the "Joomla frontpage" menu item to see the demo of this. 

The template includes heavy CSS overrides the the Joomanager component and 3 of its modules. We've included several of our S5 modules such as the Image and Content Fader and Tab show which we also have overridden with CSS stylings. Custom highlight font, colors and much more!
